wikimedia-org-welcome: Mechiro maota! Wikipedia, poroshe neri kikanga kya bandu babakola kuuma kwe hanga "connaissance" ne shanchayo ku busha.
wikimedia-org-welcome-subtitle: Sheukole kuuma netwe kwebula mbu abumenyi boshe bumenyibwe na kinsi mundu, na kinsi handu.
wikimedia-org-our-projects-desc: Asaporoshe setu siri mwa Wikimedia movement. Asaporoshe nene soshi siri mwa Wikimedia Foundation, na byobirimo abikolwa na bandu balengitse 260,000 ineulu babakolesa logiciel MediaWiki.
wikimedia-org-wmf: Wikimedia Foundation, asibele yoinabika asaporoshe wiki soshi, neasikya asanganda ineulu koshi kwe hanga bumenyi ne xunga bo bútatung.
wikimedia-org-donate-title: Amukoro awe alanga asadurwa sa bandu, kwebula mbu abumenyi buhikire kinsi mundu
wikimedia-org-contact-text: uwete lubutso kuluenda Wikimedia Foundation neri asaporoshe sa Wiki? Karibwako.
